    <item>
      <title>农业衰退将持续至 2025 年，给机械制造商 AGCO 带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/farm-slump-dragging-into-2025-to-weigh-on-machinery-maker-agco</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农业机械制造商美国爱科集团 (AGCO Corp.) 股价出现一个多月来最大跌幅，该公司表示，由于农民继续面临农作物价格低迷的困扰，该公司明年将面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/farm-slump-dragging-into-2025-to-weigh-on-machinery-maker-agco</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 17:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行不会让数据“噪音”阻碍其宽松路径</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bank-of-england-won-t-let-data-noise-knock-it-from-easing-path</link>
      <description><![CDATA[过去两年，英国通胀冲击的大部分时间里，英国央行的政策都是根据工资和物价数据的波动做出反应。而现在，央行的政策则更加依赖其自身的预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/bank-of-england-won-t-let-data-noise-knock-it-from-easing-path</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 17:02:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
